OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, the former Towie
OL,7,Fstar explained how she was
OL,8,F"devastated" when she found out what
OL,9,Fhad happened to her six-year-old son
OL,10,Fat a different rink
OL,12,FChildren will have to wear gloves at
OL,13,FPlanet Ice skating rinks after The
OL,14,FOnly Way Is Essex star Chloe Lewis
OL,15,Fstarted a petition when her six-year-
OL,16,Fold son lost part of a finger on the
OL,17,Fice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
