OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772561166
OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FMs Lewis' son, Beau, was rushed to the
OL,7,Fhospital on New Year's Eve after he
OL,8,Ffell over and another skater
OL,9,Faccidentally skated over his finger.
OL,11,FIn a post on Instagram last month,
OL,12,FChloe told her almost one million
OL,13,Ffollowers: "I didn't know whether to
OL,14,Fshare this with the world or not, as
OL,15,Fhe's my baby & as a parent you're
OL,16,Falways protective over your child.
OL,18,F"I'm sharing to help others and raise
OL,19,Fawareness."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772561166
OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FMs Lewis wrote that Beau had to
OL,7,Fundergo surgery lasting three and a
OL,8,Fhalf hours.
OL,10,FNow Planet Ice, the biggest ice rink
OL,11,Foperator in the UK, has decided to
OL,12,Fchange its rules.
OL,14,FThere will be "mandatory standard
OL,15,Fglove wearing for children under 12 at
OL,16,Fall Planet Ice rinks throughout the UK
OL,17,Ffrom June 1," the company said in a
OL,18,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
