FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772561166
OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FPlanet Ice will have gloves available
OL,7,Fto rent for a fee, or skaters will be
OL,8,Fallowed to bring their own.
OL,10,F"Glove wearing will be policed by on-
OL,11,Fice stewards throughout skating
OL,12,Fsessions," the organisation added.
OL,14,FThe incident with Ms Lewis's son did
OL,15,Fnot happen at one of their venues. The
OL,16,FTowie star is now trying to take this
OL,17,Fone step further, launching a petition
OL,18,Ffor the government to make glove-
OL,19,Fwearing compulsory across all ice-
OL,20,Fskating rinks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
