PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772561166
OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,F"I'm never going to be able to bring
OL,7,Fhis finger back, but the only thing
OL,8,FI'm going to be able to do to make him
OL,9,Fremember this in a good light is that
OL,10,Fhopefully one day, we can change the
OL,11,Flaw for other people," she told ITV
OL,12,FNews.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, the former Towie
OL,15,Fstar explained how she was
OL,16,F"devastated" when she found out what
OL,17,Fhad happened to her six-year-old son
OL,18,Fat a different rink, initially
OL,19,Fdeciding against posting the news
OL,20,Fonline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
