OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FAt the time of writing, the petition
OL,7,Fhas more than 23,200 signatures.
OL,9,F"It blows my mind, I don't know how
OL,10,Fit's not in place already," she said.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
