PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772561166
OL,3,CFormer Towie star demands new law
OL,4,Cafter son loses finger on ice rink
OL,6,FThe post on the petition website
OL,7,Freads: "I'd like to for the law to be
OL,8,Fchanged so children are only permitted
OL,9,Fto ice skate if wearing protective
OL,10,Fgloves to protect their hands. The
OL,11,Fblades are so sharp."
OL,13,FThe government responds to all
OL,14,Fpetitions that get more than 10,000
OL,15,Fsignatures, and at 100,000 signatures,
OL,16,Fpetitions are considered for debate in
OL,17,FParliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
